---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Resources" description="Insights, guides, and practical advice on AI adoption for FQHCs, rural hospitals, and community health organizations.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-badge">Resources</div>
      <h1>AI Insights for Healthcare Leaders</h1>
      <p>Practical guidance on AI adoption for FQHCs, rural hospitals, and community health organizations. No jargon, no hype — just what you need to make informed decisions.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Articles -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="articles-grid">

        <article class="article-card featured">
          <div class="article-accent blue"></div>
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">AI Readiness</span>
            <h2>5 Signs Your FQHC Is Ready for AI</h2>
            <p>AI readiness isn't about having the latest technology. It's about having the right foundation. Here are five indicators that your health center is ready to start — and what to do if you're not there yet.</p>
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span>By Tyler Wallace, Ph.D.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <div class="article-accent green"></div>
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Training</span>
            <h2>Why Generic AI Training Fails in Healthcare</h2>
            <p>Most AI training programs are built for enterprise tech teams. Here's why that doesn't work for healthcare organizations — and what to look for instead.</p>
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span>By Tyler Wallace, Ph.D.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <div class="article-accent mint"></div>
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Strategy</span>
            <h2>Microsoft Copilot for Rural Hospitals: Where to Start</h2>
            <p>You've got the licenses. Now what? A practical guide to deploying Microsoft 365 Copilot in a rural hospital setting, from quick wins to long-term adoption strategy.</p>
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span>By Tyler Wallace, Ph.D.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <div class="article-accent peach"></div>
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Industry</span>
            <h2>What the Rural Health Transformation Program Means for Your AI Strategy</h2>
            <p>The $50 billion RHTP is bringing new technology expectations to healthcare organizations nationwide. Here's how to position your organization to lead rather than scramble.</p>
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span>By Tyler Wallace, Ph.D.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="article-card">
          <div class="article-accent blue"></div>
          <div class="article-body">
            <span class="article-tag">Power BI</span>
            <h2>Moving Beyond Spreadsheets: Power BI for FQHC Reporting</h2>
            <p>UDS reporting, quality metrics, and operational dashboards — all built in tools you already pay for. A look at how FQHCs are replacing manual Excel workflows with Power BI.</p>
            <div class="article-meta">
              <span>By Tyler Wallace, Ph.D.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="section-inner section-center">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Want to talk through your AI strategy?</h2>
        <p>These articles scratch the surface. If you're ready for a deeper conversation about what AI adoption looks like for your specific organization, let's connect.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Schedule a Conversation <span class="arrow">&rarr;</span></a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-blue);
    background: rgba(15, 15, 189, 0.07);
    padding: 0.375rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Articles */
  .articles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .article-card {
    display: flex;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .article-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .article-accent {
    width: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .article-accent.blue { background: var(--color-blue); }
  .article-accent.green { background: var(--color-green); }
  .article-accent.mint { background: var(--color-blue-light); }
  .article-accent.peach { background: var(--color-peach); }

  .article-body {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .article-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .article-card h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .article-card.featured h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .article-card p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .article-meta {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-500);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--color-gray-50);
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 3.5rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    }

    .page-hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
